
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BLOGIFY</title>
    <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  />


  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">


    <style>
    * {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

body {
  line-height: 1.6;
  background: #f9f9f9;
  color: #333;
}

.container {
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: auto;
}

/* Header */
header {
  background: #1f1f1f;
  color: white;
  padding: 1rem 0;
}

.logo {
  float: left;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: bold;
}

nav ul {
  float: right;
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

nav a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

nav a:hover {
  color: #00bcd4;
  text-decoration: none;
}

header::after {
  content: "";
  display: table;
  clear: both;
}


/* Posts */
.posts-section {
  padding: 3rem 0;
}

.posts {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.post {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 5px;
  padding: 1rem;
  flex: 1 1 45%;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.post img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

.post h3 {
  margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
}

.post a {
  color: #00bcd4;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}
/* Profile Image Small */
  .profile-img {
    width: 35px;
    height: 35px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Dropdown Window */
  .dropdown-window {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 55px;
    right: 0;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    width: 220px;
    padding: 1rem;
    z-index: 1000;
  }

  /* Profile Info */
  .profile-info {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .profile-img-large {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .name {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .email {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: gray;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Dropdown Links */
  .dropdown-link {
    display: block;
    color: #333;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  .dropdown-link:hover {
    background: #e9ecef;
  }

  /* Logout Button */
  .logout-btn {
    display: block;
    background: #dc3545;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .logout-btn:hover {
    background: #b52a36;
  }

  /* Position Fix */
  .profile-dropdown {
    position: relative;
  }

/* Footer */
footer {
  background: #1f1f1f;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1rem 0;
}

  
  /* About Card Styles */
  .about-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 70vh;
    
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .about-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 90%;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-header h2 {
    color: #1f1f1f;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-header h2::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #00bcd4;
  }
  
  .about-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
  }
  
  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-content strong {
    color: #00bcd4;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-card {
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 1rem;
    }
    
    .about-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .about-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="logo">BLOGIFY</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/posts">Posts</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
         <% if (locals.user) { %>
          <!-- Add Blog Link -->
          <li><a href="/blog/add-newblog">Add Blog</a></li>

          <!-- Profile Dropdown -->
          <li class="profile-dropdown">
            <img src="<%= locals.user.profileImageURL || '/default-avatar.png' %>"
                 alt=<%= locals.user.fullname %> class="profile-img" id="profileBtn">

            <!-- Dropdown Window -->
            <div class="dropdown-window" id="profileMenu">
              <div class="profile-info">
                <img src="<%= locals.user.profileImageURL || '/default-avatar.png' %>" alt="Profile" class="profile-img-large">
                <p class="name"><%= locals.user.name %></p>
                <% if (locals.user.email) { %>
                  <p class="email"><%= locals.user.email %></p>
                <% } %>
              </div>
              <a href="/user/my-blogs" class="dropdown-link">My Blogs</a>
              <a href="/user/my-comments" class="dropdown-link">My Comments</a>
              <a href="/user/edit-profile" class="dropdown-link">Edit Profile</a>
              <a href="/user/logout" class="logout-btn">Logout</a>
            </div>
          </li>
        <% } else { %>
          <!-- Show Login if no user -->
          <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <% } %>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-card">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>BLOGIFY</strong> — a space where creativity meets clarity.  
        We are passionate about sharing insights, ideas, and stories that inspire and inform.  
        Whether you’re here to learn something new, stay updated, or just explore, our aim is to deliver content that’s engaging, authentic, and valuable.  
        <br><br>
        Our mission is simple: to connect people with meaningful content.  
        We believe that knowledge should be accessible, conversations should be open, and stories should be shared.  
        Thank you for being part of our journey — your presence here makes our work worthwhile.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 mx-auto mt-3">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase mb-4 font-weight-bold text-primary">BLOGIFY</h5>
        <p>
          A simple blogging platform for developers to share their thoughts, tutorials, and tech explorations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 mx-auto mt-3">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase mb-4 font-weight-bold text-primary">Quick Links</h5>
        <p><a href="/" class="text-dark text-decoration-none">Home</a></p>
        <p><a href="/blog/add-newblog" class="text-dark text-decoration-none">Add Blog</a></p>
        <p><a href="/login" class="text-dark text-decoration-none">Login</a></p>
        <p><a href="/signin" class="text-dark text-decoration-none">Register</a></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 mx-auto mt-3">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase mb-4 font-weight-bold text-primary">Contact</h5>
        <p><i class="bi bi-house-door-fill me-2"></i> Pune, India</p>
        <p><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill me-2"></i> vedashrisatle@gmail.com</p>
        <p><i class="bi bi-phone-fill me-2"></i> +91 XXXXXXXXXX</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <hr class="mb-4"/>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 MyBlog. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
        <div class="text-center text-md-right">
          <a href="#" class="text-dark me-3"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
          <a href="#" class="text-dark me-3"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i></a>
          <a href="#" class="text-dark me-3"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
          <a href="#" class="text-dark"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

    
</body>
</html>
